        <abstract> 
<p>Requests seeds of <hi rend="italic">Solanum rostratum</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Fritz Müller believes that in plants with anthers of different colours, bees collect from one set alone.</p> 
<p>Suggests JET send copy of paper ["Flowers of <hi rend="italic">Solanum rostratum</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Cassia chamaecrista</hi>", <hi rend="italic">Am. Nat.</hi> 16 (1882): 281–7] to Müller.</p> 
        </abstract>
